<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="96" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="3.[103,753,960,1114]" pageId="3" pageNumber="96">
The specimen [G00307102] has not been annotated as 
<taxonomicName form="apaense" pageId="3" pageNumber="96" rank="form">
form 
<emphasis box="[103,190,992,1016]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="96">apaense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by Hassler, but it is the only one with leaf and flowers and thus the only specimen matching the protologue. The specimen [G00307101] was annotated by Hassler but it does not include any leaf material.
</paragraph>
